metadata.name: Cypress Edition – Page of Swords
metadata.description:
RELIX – Cypress Edition

Page of Swords

Nascent Air nature. When an idea is new, it generates immense excitement within the mind. Countless imagined outcomes stimulate synapses and build out even more new ideas. When that energy is someone’s predominant characteristic, you have your Page of Swords. This is not someone (or an approach) you want in control of an idea’s advanced development. Alternatively, if the idea has grown stagnant, then a fresh and untested direction becomes necessary for progress.

Designed by Jiminie Ha & Jeremy Parker 
Text by Michael George Land 
More info at wolfhouse.art
